{"tid":2443209,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法國雲端服務公司OVHcloud數據中心大火 致數百萬網站癱瘓","createTime":"2021-03-12T02:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T02:44:33.000Z","uid":267658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e357b982903c94800098801de2b80e9f98d545c0","tid":2443209,"uid":267658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T02:06:01.000Z","msg":"法國雲端服務公司OVHcloud數據中心大火 致數百萬網站癱瘓<br />\n17 小時前<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/3/1615450319_4z-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F3%2F1615450319_4z-1280w.jpg&h=85da2457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOVHcloud史特拉斯堡數據中心大火。(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/3/1615450323_E8-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F3%2F1615450323_E8-1280w.jpg&h=42001474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n火勢猛烈。(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/3/1615450316_AZ-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F3%2F1615450316_AZ-1280w.jpg&h=bbe70b7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防射水灌救。(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/3/1615450312_JH-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F3%2F1615450312_JH-1280w.jpg&h=91c7728d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n數據中心被焚毀。(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n法國大型雲端服務公司OVHcloud的數據中心於當地時間周三凌晨失火，導致數百萬網站癱瘓，當中包括政府機構、銀行、商店和新聞機構網站，<a href=\"http://亦殃及法國的.FR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BA%A6%E6%AE%83%E5%8F%8A%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84.FR&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw60GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=12714da0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">亦殃及法國的.FR</a>網域，客戶擔心資料遺失。<br />\n<br />\nOVHcloud表示，該公司設於史特拉斯堡(Strasbourg)一座數據中心被大火焚毀，另一數據中心亦損毀。報道指，消防部門出動約100名消防員，終在清晨時份將火勢撲滅。<br />\n<br />\nOVHcloud在史特拉斯堡有4座數據中心，其暫未說明起火原因，兩天前才披露將首次公開招股(IPO)的計劃。1999年創立的OVHcloud，提供網站主機及諸如電子郵件及其他運算資源等內部系統，在全球各地設立數據中心。<br />\n<br />\n部分客戶表示，受事件影響，他們的網站斷線或無法取得電郵，暫未收到大量數據遺失的報告。受事件影響，法國知名的龐比度藝術中心的網站無法運作，加密貨幣交易商Deribit則表示，其博客網頁故障，但加密貨幣交易未受影響。<a href=\"http://免費弈棋網站Lichess.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E5%BC%88%E6%A3%8B%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99Lichess.org&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw60GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=365c9b7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">免費弈棋網站Lichess.org</a>表示，遺失了24小時的遊戲紀錄，新聞機構eeNews Europe的網站亦癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\nOVHcloud就事件向客戶道歉，並承諾將盡量在周四以前讓該兩座因失火受損的數據中心恢復部分運作，第三座受影響的中心則料於周五前。OVHcloud表示，約1.2萬至1.6萬用戶受影響。"},{"pid":"62f2aff3928c18068d45b4901a364937b30317df","tid":2443209,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T02:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />禾D 礦牙"},{"pid":"2c81c05b3213e88261aad0b6ddedb79e919ded2d","tid":2443209,"uid":106027,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T02:12:26.000Z","msg":"假HA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041d6d055b4c32964a4b3c3bd7a77a520df05b5b","tid":2443209,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T02:15:49.000Z","msg":"數據已被炸毁"},{"pid":"3063c18f055cab3b4142b20b3775794f8871c096","tid":2443209,"uid":306664,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T02:23:34.000Z","msg":"日落到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我宣布eu係第三世界國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401dbc7c9cb0fc0a3f57fa48a23a4aa3e76f2d6f","tid":2443209,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T02:26:16.000Z","msg":"咁似gta v 果棟停車場嘅"},{"pid":"